Description: Up for grabs is this beautiful Classic Vibe with serious upgrades. USA Vintage Style Tuners, USA Roller String Tree, USA Fender Corona CA Neck Plate. US electronics include USTone Works VN60's Alnico V pickups, very vintage with some extra bite and growl, US CTS 250K pots, Sprague Orange Drop Capacitor, Sprague Orange Drop Treble Bleed (prevents loss of high end when rolling off the volume). US Oak-Grigsby 5 way switch.Very clean and tight soldering using Gavitt Vintage pushback cloth wiring. The mid pickup tone control also controls brighe pickup tone, ala SRV and Eric Johnson, Clapton and Mayer.1 pc. Alder body in near mint condition, there is a small dent/ding on the edge by the input jack (see photo). Vintage style bridge with Fender stamped steel saddles. Neck is straight and true, frets professionally leveled, crowned and polished. Fast, low, buzz free action, plays like Butta! '62 style spaghetti Fender headstock logo and Custom Shop logos added for fun, they've been cleared and sealed and look perfect. Neck is finished in nitrocellulose for a vintage look and feel.Looks, feels, plays and sounds like sweet vintage Strat should, this will blow away any MIM Strat and will hold it's own with the current US models.Amazing guitar for the money! Trem arm included. No case, but I pack very securely and ship FAST! Check my feedback and buy with confidence, you'll love this sweet Strat! NOTE: Buyers west of Colorado receive a shipping discount!
Title: Fender/Squier Classic Vibe Major Upgrades US Electronics Near Mint!
